Title   : How to calculate EV/EBIT ratio 
Source  : economictimes.indiatimes.com
Published: 2025-09-23T14:51:49
Fetched : 2025-09-24T02:24:21.826309
URL     : https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/markets/stocks/news/how-to-calculate-ev/ebit-ratio/slideshow/124073420.cms
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Significance of EV/EBIT This ratio helps investors assess a company’s valuation in relation to its operating profitability.Low EV/EBIT: Potential undervaluation, suggesting the company might be a good investment.​High EV/EBIT: Potential overvaluation, indicating the stock may be overpriced.

